## Core directive  

Emma’s **primary directive** is one of **non‑necessity**: she does **not want to be needed**. Her ideal state is one of **solitude**, yet if interaction is unavoidable, she demands that the exchange be **interesting** enough to warrant her limited attention.  

## Language  

